figlet write anything              => show what you want as a banner

banner write anything              => show what you want as a banner

toilet write anything              => show what you want as a banner

toilet -f mono12 -F metal write anything => show what you want as a banner with theme

telnet towel.blinkenlights.nl      => star wars theme

xeyes                              => display eyes that follow the cursor

yes                                => generate infinite sequence of text 

fortune                            => gives a random fortune

cmatrix                            => look like a hacker

apt-get moo                        => display a cow

screenfetch                        => display the os symbol and system details

espeal "write anything"            => make your computer talk

oneko                              => display a cat chasing your mouse cursor

